Package com.esri.mo2.ext.img

Classes collection to support read/write for different image formats.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BMPImageWriter An ImageWriter implementation that write BMP format.
BNDImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads BIL/BIP/BSQ format.
DummyImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads OVL/L format to support "ovl" and "l" file extention for ArcIMS compatibility.
GISImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads GIS/LAN format.
ImagefileHandler This implementation of FileHandler provides support for various images formats.
IMGImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads ERDAS IMG format.
JAIImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads TIF/BMP/JPEG/PNG/GIF format.
JPEGImageWriter An ImageWriter implementation that write JPEG format.
MrSIDImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads MrSID format.
NITFImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads NITF format.
PNGImageWriter An ImageWriter implementation that write JPEG format.
RLCImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads RLC format.
SUNImageReader An ImageReader implementation that reads SUN format.
 

Package com.esri.mo2.ext.img Description

Classes collection to support read/write for different image formats.
